OL,3,CCouncillors resign from Labour party
OL,4,Cover 'bullying' claims
OL,6,FTwenty councillors and their leader
OL,7,Fhave resigned from the after accusing
OL,8,Fits national leadership of bullying.
OL,10,FThe group in , , say the party is
OL,11,F"targeting local councillors" by
OL,12,F"preventing them from standing for
OL,13,Felections" and "using aggressive
OL,14,Fbullying tactics to suppress fairness
OL,15,Fand free speech".
OL,17,FThe councillors, including Pendle
OL,18,FBorough leader Asjad Mahmood, will
OL,19,Fform independent groups on Pendle
OL,20,FBorough Council, Brierfield Town
OL,21,FCouncil, and Nelson Town Council.
