OL,6,FCouncillor Mahmood, now the leader of
OL,7,Fthe independent group, said, "I, along
OL,8,Fwith my colleagues, were elected by
OL,9,Flocal residents to represent them in
OL,10,Fthe council chamber.
OL,12,F"As a Labour Councillor, I have always
OL,13,Ffelt that the party's policies were
OL,14,Faligned with my own beliefs and those
OL,15,Fof the constituents who have honoured
OL,16,Fme with their votes.
