OL,6,F"I, for one, cannot stand by and allow
OL,7,Fthis to happen. The bullying needs to
OL,8,Fstop."
OL,10,FThe resignations come six months after
OL,11,Fthe leader of Pendle and Burnley
OL,12,Fcouncils .
OL,14,FA Labour Party Spokesperson said: "The
OL,15,FLabour Party's focus is on winning the
OL,16,FGeneral Election so we can improve the
OL,17,Flives of those we are elected to
OL,18,Fserve."
